 <summary>Provides a standard interface to manipulate images, this is the IM driver</summary>
 <description>This package was written to provide a simpler and cross-library interface to doing image transformations and manipulations.
This is the imagemagick driver, doesn't utilize the imagick PHP exts but instead interacts straight with the CLI of Imagemagick which
is not recommended.

It provides :

* grayscale
* files related functions
* addText
* Scale (by length, percentage, maximum X/Y)
* Resize
* Rotate (custom angle)
* Crop
* Mirror
* Flip
 </description>
